Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.24,0:00:01.44,中文,,0,0,0,,血族上集回顾\NPreviously on The Strain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.44,0:00:03.44,中文,,0,0,0,,啊 儿子\NAh, mi hijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.46,0:00:05.34,中文,,0,0,0,,两个孩子都回家了 真好\NSo good to have my two kids together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.34,0:00:06.24,中文,,0,0,0,,要我跟你说多少次\NHow many times I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.24,0:00:08.69,中文,,0,0,0,,别把垃圾留在走道里\NDon't leave your recycling in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:10.34,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要谈谈你对我妈妈说话的态度\NNow we're talking about the way you speak to my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.34,0:00:13.34,中文,,0,0,0,,如果她再告诉我 你用这种态度跟她说话\NIf she ever tells me you talk to her like that again,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.34,0:00:14.94,中文,,0,0,0,,那别人就会在那些你最爱的垃圾桶里\Nthey're gonna find your body
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.94,0:00:17.44,中文,,0,0,0,,找到你的尸体\Nin one of those recycling bins you love so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:20.66,中文,,0,0,0,,棺材里面是什么 土壤\NWhat was in that coffin? Soil...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:22.64,中文,,0,0,0,,那个橱柜去哪儿了\NWhere's that cabinet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:23.74,中文,,0,0,0,,那箱子有500磅重\NThat box was 500 pounds;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.74,0:00:25.14,中文,,0,0,0,,不可能那样把它举起来的\Nnothing could lift it up like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.42,0:00:27.23,中文,,0,0,0,,棺材在你们手上 那么他也在你们手上\NIf you have the coffin, then you still have him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.23,0:00:29.44,中文,,0,0,0,,别让他渡过河\NDo not allow it across the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:32.75,中文,,0,0,0,,某种邪恶的东西在这里蔓延 老鼠一般是不会这么大批出洞的\NSomething evil has taken root. Rats don't migrate like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.75,0:00:34.59,中文,,0,0,0,,有东西在把他们赶出地底下\NSomething's driving them out from underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:36.97,中文,,0,0,0,,那东西深藏在底下黑暗处\NIt's hiding down there in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:39.18,中文,,0,0,0,,我搜了空荡鼠穴的中心地带\NI tracked the epicenter of the rat-free zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:41.54,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要检查所有世贸中心附近\NWe have to look at all the decommissioned tunnels
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:43.03,中文,,0,0,0,,的拆除了的隧道\Nnear the World Trade Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:45.59,中文,,0,0,0,,消灭掉血祖 他的爪牙们也难逃一死\NKill the Master, and his spawn will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:48.03,中文,,0,0,0,,他们来了\NThey're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:51.92,中文,,0,0,0,,额 好的\NUh... Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:55.04,中文,,0,0,0,,紫外炸弹测试\NUV light bomb test.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:00:59.45,中文,,0,0,0,,{\pos(932,578)} {\fs50\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\pos(1028,574)}{\fade(0,500)} 哈莱姆区 东118街
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:01:00.41,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 不不不 过来 来\NHey! No, no, no. Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:07.75,中文,,0,0,0,,- 那我什么都看不到了 - 这就对了\N- Now I can't see anything. - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:08.78,中文,,0,0,0,,总比让紫外射线\NIt's better than burning
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:10.54,中文,,0,0,0,,烧伤你的视网膜要好\Nout your retinas looking at the UVC rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:11.89,中文,,0,0,0,,真不公平\NNo fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:14.47,中文,,0,0,0,,这真的是个好主意么\NThis is a... good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.24,0:01:19.30,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们正要看看是不是\NWell, we're about to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.53,0:01:21.18,中文,,0,0,0,,小心炸弹\NFire in the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.97,0:01:29.82,中文,,0,0,0,,咱最好把火灭了\NYou might want to put that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:38.69,中文,,0,0,0,,- 什么情况 - 用工程术语讲 呃\N- What happened? - In engineering terms, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.02,0:01:40.74,中文,,0,0,0,,就是 测试失败了\Nyou'd call that a fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:42.33,中文,,0,0,0,,史诗级的失败\NAn epic fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:45.24,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 在持续的时间里 紫外光还是挺强的\NWell, light was strong while it lasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.24,0:01:48.21,中文,,0,0,0,,- 持续时间足够得长来伤害到人吗 - 也许要更长\N- Was it long enough to hurt them? - Could be bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:50.24,中文,,0,0,0,,要让灯泡足够亮才行\NNeed to keep the bulbs bright enough to do the job
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:52.28,中文,,0,0,0,,同时又不会过快地烧坏\Nwithout burning them out so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.28,0:01:53.28,中文,,0,0,0,,如果是我\NWell if it were me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:55.21,中文,,0,0,0,,我会让灯泡周期性亮暗闪烁\NI would make the lights cycle on and off,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:56.79,中文,,0,0,0,,就像照相机里的闪光灯\Nstrobe like a camera flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.79,0:01:59.23,中文,,0,0,0,,这样灯泡就不会烧坏了\NThat might stop the bulbs from burning out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:03.93,中文,,0,0,0,,我还装一台喷雾机 你懂的 再打点鼓\NI could rig up a fog machine too, you know, crank some tunes,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:06.17,中文,,0,0,0,,这样我们就可以跳街舞了 就像 嘣 嘣 嘣\Nreally get 'em dancing. Just boom, boom, boom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:06.79,中文,,0,0,0,,那当我没说\NForget I mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:10.21,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你还想不想 - 我在开玩笑啊 博士\N- Do what you want. - I'm just joking, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:15.80,中文,,0,0,0,,我没说不同意 因为我确实赞成你的想法\NI'm not saying I disagree because I do agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:18.05,中文,,0,0,0,,别从你的高头大马上掉下来\NDon't fall off your high horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.28,中文,,0,0,0,,问题是 是\NProblem is, is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.82,0:02:24.40,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们没法再做测试了\Nwell, we can't do any more tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:27.36,中文,,0,0,0,,我可以安上我剩下的灯泡\NI could put the rest of our bulbs in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:31.52,中文,,0,0,0,,把电路板补好 装个振荡器\Ntinker with the circuit board, put in an oscillator...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:34.71,中文,,0,0,0,,但我们还得从这堆烂摊子开始\NBut we're gonna have to go with what we end up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:36.79,中文,,0,0,0,,- 希望没啥问题 - 费茨先生\N- Hope for the best. - Mr. Fet,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:39.38,中文,,0,0,0,,你刚描述的那种方法\Nyou've just described my method of operation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:41.67,中文,,0,0,0,,我过去用了60年\Nfor the past six decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:03.58,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈 你在做什么\NMama, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:08.80,中文,,0,0,0,,这该死的厨房里什么都找不到\NI can't find anything in this damn kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:12.56,中文,,0,0,0,,显然她是在找她之前的那个\NApparently she's searching for an ashtray she once owned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.57,0:03:15.57,中文,,0,0,0,,从布宜诺斯艾利斯的阿拉维尔酒店里得到的烟灰缸\Nfrom the Alvear Hotel, Buenos Aires.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:18.47,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道就在这儿的什么地方\NI know it's here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:20.85,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈\NMama...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:24.48,中文,,0,0,0,,那个多年前就坏了 嗯\Nthat broke years ago. Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.78,中文,,0,0,0,,我来收拾干净\NI'll clean it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:34.72,中文,,0,0,0,,这儿不是你自己的厨房\NThis is not your kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:42.21,中文,,0,0,0,,这里有个烟灰缸\NAn ashtray here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:45.82,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:53.11,中文,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢他\NI don't like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:56.23,中文,,0,0,0,,塞特拉基安先生是这里的主人\NMr. Setrakian is our host.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.96,中文,,0,0,0,,他的灵魂好黑暗\NHe has a dark soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:00.07,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈 够了\NMama, basta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:02.05,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈够了 我们是客人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.01,中文,,0,0,0,,你这样不礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:17.55,中文,,0,0,0,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:19.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我理解她所经历的一切\NI understand what she's experiencing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:21.78,中文,,0,0,0,,她做的不对 她关于你的说法也不对\NShe's wrong, what she said about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:24.77,中文,,0,0,0,,不 她是对的\NNo, she's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.33,中文,,0,0,0,,你妈妈还好吗\NIs your mother going to be OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:33.04,中文,,0,0,0,,有时候她会犯糊涂\NShe gets confused sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:35.85,中文,,0,0,0,,她会混淆记忆和现实中的事儿\NShe mistakes memories for reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:38.39,中文,,0,0,0,,她一定很喜欢那个烟灰缸\NShe must have really liked that ashtray.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:42.81,中文,,0,0,0,,是一个酒店里弄到的\NIt was from a hotel-restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:45.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我父亲第一次和她约会的地方\Nwhere my father took her on their first date.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:48.74,中文,,0,0,0,,他想要一个纪念品 因为他那个时候就知道\NHe wanted a memento, because he knew right then,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:51.78,中文,,0,0,0,,从第一个晚上开始就知道 他一定会娶她\Nfrom that first night, that he was gonna marry her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:55.00,中文,,0,0,0,,这样的话 也许她记得这事儿 也是好的\NWell then, maybe it's good that she still remembers it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:57.36,中文,,0,0,0,,我想你是对的\NI think you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:06.49,中文,,0,0,0,,{\pos(334,558)} {\fs50\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\pos(1028,574)}{\fade(0,500)} 哈莱姆区 东115街
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:09.71,中文,,0,0,0,,克里斯宾 开门\NCrispin, open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:15.46,中文,,0,0,0,,克里斯宾 该死的开门啊 我不是在玩 哥们儿\NCrispin, open the damn door! I'm not playing, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:28.34,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈\NMama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:53.76,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈呢\NWhere's Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:58.51,中文,,0,0,0,,克里斯宾 你听到了吗 妈妈在哪儿\NCrispin, do you hear me? Where is Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:54.38,中文,,0,0,0,,不\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:56.54,中文,,0,0,0,,不 不\NNo! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:05.16,中文,,0,0,0,,首先 别伤害到人\NFirst, do no harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:07.59,中文,,0,0,0,,情况不一样了\NThings have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:09.65,中文,,0,0,0,,真的吗\NHave they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:12.98,中文,,0,0,0,,好比说一个遥远的村庄 比如200多年前的\NTake a remote village, say 200 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:16.52,中文,,0,0,0,,村民们出现了奇怪的症状\NResidents are manifesting strange symptoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:19.18,中文,,0,0,0,,死亡 恐惧 迷信 四处弥漫\NDying, fear and superstition rule the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:22.79,中文,,0,0,0,,人们说村子遭到了诅咒 直到有一天就像你和我一样的人出现了\Nand a curse is blamed until someone like you or me shows up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:25.66,中文,,0,0,0,,然后 通过一系列科学的方法\Nand, through a scientific process of elimination,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:29.15,中文,,0,0,0,,我们找到了瘟疫的源头 消灭了它\Ntraces the disease to a source and destroys it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:33.23,中文,,0,0,0,,诅咒解除 人民得救\NThe curse is lifted. People are saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:34.87,中文,,0,0,0,,秩序重建\NOrder is restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:37.04,中文,,0,0,0,,就是说你现在也相信了\NSo you believe now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:40.20,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们把血祖杀了 那么这场吸血鬼瘟疫\NIf we slay the Master, this plague of vampirism
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:42.65,中文,,0,0,0,,- 就能结束 - 我只能相信\N- ends today? - I have to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:45.95,中文,,0,0,0,,不然 我也不会把扎克留在这儿\NOtherwise, I can't justify leaving Zach here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:48.81,中文,,0,0,0,,冒着成为孤儿的险\Nat the risk of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:54.55,中文,,0,0,0,,或是更糟糕\Nbeing orphaned or worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:58.89,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我们会成功会回来的 - 万一我们回不来呢\N- We'll make it back here. - What if we don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:05.59,中文,,0,0,0,,也许我们中的一个要留下\NMaybe one of us should stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:07.78,中文,,0,0,0,,你是说我\NYou mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:11.54,中文,,0,0,0,,我绝不会要你留下\NI would never ask you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:13.19,中文,,0,0,0,,你刚就说了\NYou just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:18.27,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我的答案是不 - 我不是那个意思\N- The answer is no. - I didn't mean it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:20.15,中文,,0,0,0,,我把我妈妈留着这里了\NI'm leaving my mother behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.15,0:08:21.85,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道我知道\NI know, I know you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.91,0:08:25.15,中文,,0,0,0,,我们俩不是刺客\NYou and I are not assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:28.72,中文,,0,0,0,,费特 那个杀戮为乐的除害师\NFet, that kill-happy exterminator,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:31.08,中文,,0,0,0,,这个神风任务只是他的白日梦\Nthis kamikaze mission is his wet dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:33.04,中文,,0,0,0,,那老头也被古老的仇恨所侵蚀\NAnd the old man is consumed by an ancient grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:34.31,中文,,0,0,0,,他们没有备用计划\NThey hace no plan B,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:36.49,中文,,0,0,0,,因为他们只能自己去冒这个险\Nbecause they have no one but themselves at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:39.69,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们别无选择\NI don't think we have any other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:15.40,中文,,0,0,0,,这是金 肯特特的武器\NThis was the weapon Jim Kent chose to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:17.90,中文,,0,0,0,,由你带着 是对他的致敬\NYou would honor him by taking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:21.51,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:30.28,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你什么时候能回来 - 最晚到太阳落山\N- When will you be back? - Sundown, absolute latest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:33.42,中文,,0,0,0,,- 那就是一整天了 - 我会尽早的\N- That's the whole day! - Hopefully sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:34.86,中文,,0,0,0,,那妈妈怎么办\NWhat about mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:36.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得最好的办法就是\NI think the best thing is to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.52,0:09:39.28,中文,,0,0,0,,除掉那个\Ntake out that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:42.12,中文,,0,0,0,,引发了这一切的源头 塞特拉基安先生知道怎么做\Nthe thing that's causing all this. Mr. Setrakian has a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:44.82,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道 可为什么我不能一起去\NI understand, but why can't I come with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:48.22,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道那儿是什么情况\NI don't know what's out there. I,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:51.18,中文,,0,0,0,,我不能控制那儿的情况 但是这里\NI can't control that environment, but here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:53.12,中文,,0,0,0,,你也看到塞特拉基安先生的地下室了\NYou've seen Mr. Setrakian's basement,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:53.99,中文,,0,0,0,,简直是个堡垒\Nit's a fortress,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:55.99,中文,,0,0,0,,是个军火库 最安全的地方\Nit's an armory. It's the most safe place
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:58.72,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我能想象你在那儿很安全 - 你要小心 好吗\N- I could imagine for you. - You'll be careful, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.02,中文,,0,0,0,,当然\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:03.94,中文,,0,0,0,,我保证 同时 你要看好马丁内斯夫人\NI promise. In the meantime, keep an eye on Mrs. Martinez.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:05.61,中文,,0,0,0,,不应该是她来看好我么\NShouldn't that be the other way around?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:06.93,中文,,0,0,0,,也是\NShould be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:11.45,中文,,0,0,0,,但你是当家的 你要守在地下室里\NBut you're in charge. You stay in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:13.89,中文,,0,0,0,,你们俩都是 不要让任何人看到你们\NBoth of you. Don't let anybody see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:15.94,中文,,0,0,0,,好\NOk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:18.72,中文,,0,0,0,,该走了\NTime to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:22.36,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你很勇敢\NYou're brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:54.47,中文,,0,0,0,,我爱你\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:57.05,中文,,0,0,0,,我也爱你\NI love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:46.41,中文,,0,0,0,,孩子 我的烟灰缸在哪\NYoung boy! Where is my ashtray?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:47.61,中文,,0,0,0,,不知道 这里没有\NI don't know, it's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:49.40,中文,,0,0,0,,你把它拿到哪去了\NWhat did you do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:52.75,中文,,0,0,0,,我没碰过 等诺拉回来了她会帮你找到的\NI didn't put it anywhere. Nora can help when she comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:21.61,中文,,0,0,0,,我女儿去哪了\NWhere is my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:23.93,中文,,0,0,0,,她和其他人一起出去了\NShe went out with all the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:28.23,中文,,0,0,0,,她把我的烟也拿走了吗 我要抽烟\NIs she getting my cigarettes? I need my cigarettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:32.97,中文,,0,0,0,,你看 我要烟了\NSee? I need cigarettes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:36.73,中文,,0,0,0,,你不能 我妈说过不能抽烟的\NYou shouldn't... My mom says you shouldn't smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:41.13,中文,,0,0,0,,等诺拉回来了她会给你的\NNora will get you some when she comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:56.84,中文,,0,0,0,,赶紧拿走 快点\NLet's haul ass! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:13:02.56,中文,,0,0,0,,- 现在每个人都有的忙了 - 每个人都是自私自利的\N- Everybody's having fun now. - Every man for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.06,0:13:05.51,中文,,0,0,0,,这正是血祖所期望看到的\NThat's what the Master is counting on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:13.43,中文,,0,0,0,,快跑 快跑\NRun! Run! Run! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:23.45,中文,,0,0,0,,快接电话啊 妈妈\NC'mon, Mama, pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:27.37,中文,,0,0,0,,求你了 快接电话\NPick up, mama, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.61,0:13:48.33,中文,,0,0,0,,欢迎致电\NThank you for calling
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:49.86,中文,,0,0,0,,哈莱姆医疗中心\NHarlem's Hospital Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.86,0:13:51.83,中文,,0,0,0,,如果您知道分机号码\NIf you know your party's extension...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:57.66,中文,,0,0,0,,麻烦请瓜达卢佩 埃利萨尔德接电话\NYeah, can I speak to Guadalupe Elizalde, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:58.84,中文,,0,0,0,,我有急事\NIt's an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:14:00.49,中文,,0,0,0,,请问你是\NMay I ask who's calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:02.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我是奥古斯丁 埃利萨尔德 她的儿子\NIt's Augustine Elizalde, her son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:03.47,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 请稍等\NYeah, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:04.36,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\NOk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:09.19,中文,,0,0,0,,奥古斯丁 埃利萨尔德女士的班是到六点\NMr. Elizalde, Guadalupe's shift is until 6 pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:10.37,中文,,0,0,0,,现在这里一片混乱\NIt's totally crazy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:12.52,中文,,0,0,0,,她之前也许有来过 我不清楚\NShe might have called in early or come here early, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:13.68,中文,,0,0,0,,不过我没看见她\NBut I haven't seen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:15.04,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 谢谢了\NOK. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:32.26,中文,,0,0,0,,来人啊 救救我\NSomebody please! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:35.03,中文,,0,0,0,,我要出去\NI need to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:37.36,中文,,0,0,0,,救命\NHelp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:43.35,中文,,0,0,0,,我被关在里面了 快帮帮我\NIt's locked! Help me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:47.97,中文,,0,0,0,,帮帮我\NHelp me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:52.21,中文,,0,0,0,,求求你们了\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:56.66,中文,,0,0,0,,马丁内斯夫人\NMrs. Martinez!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:58.91,中文,,0,0,0,,你终于来了 孩子\NOh, there you are, young boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:01.64,中文,,0,0,0,,钥匙 快把钥匙给我\NThe keys! Give me the keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:06.15,中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸把钥匙给我了 你要到里面楼下去吗\NMy dad gave me the keys. Do you want to go back downstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:08.74,中文,,0,0,0,,我女儿 我的诺拉\NMy daughter, my Nora,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:11.65,中文,,0,0,0,,他们把她带走了 我必须去找她\Nthey've taken her. I must go to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:14.24,中文,,0,0,0,,不是的 她是自己跟他们一起走的 她会回来的\NNo, she left on her own. She's coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:18.57,中文,,0,0,0,,- 他们都会回来的 - 他们不会回来的 不会\N- They're all coming back! - They never come back! Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:25.38,中文,,0,0,0,,我们必须离开这里\NWe must leave this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:27.06,中文,,0,0,0,,求你了\NPlease!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:29.22,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我要离开这里地方 - 如果\N- I need to get out of here! - If I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:30.94,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我去给你找些香烟来\NIf I go get you cigarettes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:33.53,中文,,0,0,0,,你能在楼下安静地等我吗\Nwill you go downstairs and wait for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:52.55,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么是世贸中心\NWhy the World Trade Center?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.15,中文,,0,0,0,,{\pos(816,570)} {\fs50\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\pos(1028,574)} 曼哈顿 钱伯斯街车站
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:56.65,中文,,0,0,0,,血祖经常出没于人类悲惨的地方\NThe Master is drawn to places of great human misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:16:58.25,中文,,0,0,0,,他被痛苦所吸引\NHe seeks out suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:01.54,中文,,0,0,0,,食尸鬼的味道\NEau de strigoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:03.98,中文,,0,0,0,,我想我们来对地方了\NI think we're in the right place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:10.74,中文,,0,0,0,,不入虎穴\N"The cave you fear to enter...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:13.64,中文,,0,0,0,,焉得虎子\NHolds the treasure that you seek."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:27.30,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 上帝啊\NOh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:30.21,中文,,0,0,0,,马丁内斯医生 运气好的话\NWith any luck, Dr. Martinez,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:32.93,中文,,0,0,0,,前面还会遇到比这更糟的地狱\Nit's gonna get a hell of a lot messier than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:35.15,中文,,0,0,0,,都往右边靠\NStay to the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:38.34,中文,,0,0,0,,第三轨道\NThe third rail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:42.80,中文,,0,0,0,,不知道是不是在这下面 不过\NI don't know if it's live down here, but, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:45.96,中文,,0,0,0,,这可有625伏电压 最好别碰\Nthat's 625 volts; we don't want to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:07.46,中文,,0,0,0,,这些东西都代表了他们每个人的一生\NIt's everything that defined these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:09.38,中文,,0,0,0,,我可不想\NWell, I hope I'm defined
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:12.01,中文,,0,0,0,,让钱包和一块手表来总结我的人生\Nby more than just my wallet and my wristwatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:14.65,中文,,0,0,0,,你看到的每一样东西都象征着别人的母亲\NEverything you see represents somebody's mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:16.93,中文,,0,0,0,,- 父亲 儿子 女儿 - 不用跟他纠结了\N- father, son, daughter. - Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:51.11,中文,,0,0,0,,跟着一辆灰色的福特或普利茅斯\NFollowing either a gray Ford or a Plymouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:55.80,中文,,0,0,0,,正在追捕两个逃亡南方的白种男性\NWe're looking at two male Caucasians moving south...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:02.91,中文,,0,0,0,,你的手机还能用吗 有信号吗\NDoes your phone work? Can you get a signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:04.43,中文,,0,0,0,,没有 我的手机也用不了\NNo, mine doesn't work either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:14.09,中文,,0,0,0,,没有痕迹了\NNo more graffiti.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:18.24,中文,,0,0,0,,911事件后这个地方就被遗弃了\NThe station was abandoned after 9/11...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:21.36,中文,,0,0,0,,之后恐怕就没人来过这里了\NDoubt anyone's been here since.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:23.59,中文,,0,0,0,,当然我指的是活生生的人\NAnyone still human that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:58.30,中文,,0,0,0,,他们群居在这里\NThey're nesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.91,0:21:02.19,中文,,0,0,0,,通常都是在白天的时候\NDuring daylight hours, always.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:04.27,中文,,0,0,0,,尤其是第一次变异\NEspecially when first turned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:09.24,中文,,0,0,0,,变异的过程会消耗他们很多精力\NThe, uh, transformation, it exhausts them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:12.40,中文,,0,0,0,,这么多脖子够我们砍的了\NThat's a lot of necks to chop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:13.23,中文,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.11,0:21:15.05,中文,,0,0,0,,先放着不管\NReleasing them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.77,0:21:19.31,中文,,0,0,0,,不然血祖会注意到我们的存在 都关掉\Nwould alert the Master to our presence. Switch off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:48.12,中文,,0,0,0,,凯利\NKelly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:21:58.59,中文,,0,0,0,,不是她 伊弗\NEph, it's not her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:04.85,中文,,0,0,0,,我们得继续前进\NWe must keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.95,0:22:35.31,中文,,0,0,0,,要是我当时在场保护你就好了 妈妈\NI should have been there for you, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.61,0:23:10.50,中文,,0,0,0,,法雷尔先生\NMr. Farrell...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.98,0:23:13.47,中文,,0,0,0,,你是来收房租的对吧\Nyou're here for the rent, puto?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.07,0:23:21.62,中文,,0,0,0,,看 这里的轨道很干净\NLook. The rails are clean here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.82,0:23:24.35,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 给车留的\NAh, service cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.79,0:23:28.30,中文,,0,0,0,,他们用这些废弃的车站来调转方向\NThey use the abandoned stations for turnarounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:34.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我对这些地下通道可是了如指掌 这条线\NI know these tunnels like the back of my hand. Now, this line
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:38.24,中文,,0,0,0,,是建在1923年的一条老线之上的\Nwas built on top of the old original 1923 line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.05,0:23:40.38,中文,,0,0,0,,它就像\NYeah, it's like, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.88,0:23:43.61,中文,,0,0,0,,古罗马或者是耶路撒冷\Nancient Rome or the City of David.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.75,0:23:49.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我们听过很多次这种声响了 博士\NWe were hearing that the whole time, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.70,0:23:51.05,中文,,0,0,0,,不 不一样\NNo, no, this is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.17,0:23:56.09,中文,,0,0,0,,这些隧道 它们发出一些奇怪的声响\NThese tunnels, they do strange things to sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.09,0:23:57.74,中文,,0,0,0,,就像 就像一个窃窃私语的小厅\NYou know, like whispering chambers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:23:58.57,中文,,0,0,0,,知道吗\NYou know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.47,0:24:02.26,中文,,0,0,0,,如果有火车来了 我们会知道的\NIf there's a train coming, we're gonna know it, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.70,0:24:03.35,中文,,0,0,0,,快来\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.64,0:24:10.61,中文,,0,0,0,,-跑 -快跑\N- Go! - Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.96,0:24:21.17,中文,,0,0,0,,你刚说啥来着\NYou were saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.17,0:24:25.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我对这些隧道了如指掌\N"I know these tunnels like the back of my hand."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.76,0:24:27.50,中文,,0,0,0,,怕你不知道 这是你的手背\NFor future reference, that's the back of your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.50,0:24:29.25,中文,,0,0,0,,那是你的屁股 你的手肘\NThat's your ass. That's your elbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.31,0:24:31.12,中文,,0,0,0,,你想带路么\NYou want to take lead, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.21,0:24:32.32,中文,,0,0,0,,带吧\NTake point? Then go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.32,0:24:34.02,中文,,0,0,0,,随便吧 带路吧 博士\NBe my guest. Go for it, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.32,0:24:35.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我受够这个自大的家伙了\NI'm sick of this Brooklyn-pride shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.78,0:24:37.26,中文,,0,0,0,,你还是省省吧\NSave it for somebody who cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.42,0:24:39.29,中文,,0,0,0,,你是非要强辩到底了啊\NYou're used to having the last word, huh, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.35,0:24:41.74,中文,,0,0,0,,一个当铺老板或者买鼠药的人比你都知道的多\NHow does it feel to know that a pawnbroker
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.74,0:24:43.80,中文,,0,0,0,,这种感觉怎么样\Nand a rat killer know more than you do, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.80,0:24:45.32,中文,,0,0,0,,你为此等了一辈子了 是么\NYou've been waiting for this your whole life, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.32,0:24:47.77,中文,,0,0,0,,恭喜你 你的吸血鬼末日要到来了\NCongratulations on the vampire apocalypse.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.03,0:24:50.55,中文,,0,0,0,,开始即灭亡\NThe first will be last.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.66,0:24:52.58,中文,,0,0,0,,灭亡即新生 博士\NThe last shall be first, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.60,0:24:55.33,中文,,0,0,0,,够了 你们俩 注意点\NEnough! Both of you! Pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.67,0:25:14.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我们不能被发现了\NWe cannot afford to be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.20,0:25:15.02,中文,,0,0,0,,还不行\NNot yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.49,0:25:30.79,中文,,0,0,0,,真是挑的一条好路走 一群蠢货\NIt's a shitty way to go, even for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.14,0:25:34.71,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 又发现一个新方法杀死他们了\NNow, I know another way to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.49,0:25:38.23,中文,,0,0,0,,下次出来 你带上变压器\NNext outing, you carry the power transformer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.23,0:25:42.87,中文,,0,0,0,,她朝这个方向走 我们应该很近了\NShe was heading this way, so we're close.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.46,0:25:44.48,中文,,0,0,0,,小心点\NJust be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.94,0:25:49.39,中文,,0,0,0,,他们会更好一点 大规模的抢劫活动\N...or, they'll get any better. Widespread looting.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.39,0:25:51.67,中文,,0,0,0,,-紧急救援已经展开 -有人吗\N- Emergency services stretched. - Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.20,0:25:55.69,中文,,0,0,0,,公共基础设施被破坏 专家人士预测\NInfrastructure's crumbling, and there are serious concerns
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.70,0:25:59.28,中文,,0,0,0,,未来可能还会发生供水系统的瘫痪和损坏\Nthat hydro and water services are in imminent danger of collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.28,0:26:01.98,中文,,0,0,0,,此外 昨晚发来的报道\NAdded to that, last night's events,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.98,0:26:04.31,中文,,0,0,0,,在乔治华盛顿大桥上\Non the George Washington's bridge particularly,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.47,0:26:07.71,中文,,0,0,0,,最近一次警戒部署引发人民的关注\Nhas sparked concerns over a recent wave of vigilantism
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.71,0:26:10.01,中文,,0,0,0,,从而引发大规模的恐慌\Nthat has spread panic over law-abiding citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.01,0:26:11.57,中文,,0,0,0,,许多市民决定\NAnd many citizens have actually
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.57,0:26:13.90,中文,,0,0,0,,举家迁徙 搬离这个城镇\Ndecided to pull up stakes and get out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.91,0:26:16.47,中文,,0,0,0,,我们现在正连线一位准备搬家的市民\NWe have one such gentleman on the line right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.80,0:26:22.48,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 中头奖了\NOhhh, jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.78,0:26:24.83,中文,,0,0,0,,这里真是乱糟糟的\NSloppy seconds is more like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.50,0:26:26.78,中文,,0,0,0,,食物就是食物\NBut food's food.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.83,0:26:29.61,中文,,0,0,0,,检查一下收银箱\NCheck the cash register just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.61,0:26:32.10,中文,,0,0,0,,多装几袋食物 我们可以把吃不完的用来交换别的东西\NAnd grab another bag to fill. We'll trade what we can't eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.52,0:26:34.20,中文,,0,0,0,,这样的商店我们怕是找不到第二家了\NWe might not find another store like this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.21,0:26:36.45,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 该死\NOhhh... Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.13,0:26:40.13,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 维尔 这个收银员 他\NHey, Val, the clerk, he, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.22,0:26:40.95,中文,,0,0,0,,别像个胆小鬼一样\NDon't be such a pussy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.96,0:26:42.65,中文,,0,0,0,,你不想要食物了么\NYou want to eat, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.14,0:26:44.94,中文,,0,0,0,,看看储藏室 找点罐装金枪鱼\NCheck the backroom, look for canned tuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.28,0:27:53.21,中文,,0,0,0,,-噢 天呐 -放开我\N- Oh, Jesus! Hey! - Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.21,0:27:55.12,中文,,0,0,0,,你在这儿干吗 小鬼 嘿 瓦珥\NWhat are you doing here, kid? Hey, Val!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.01,0:28:00.19,中文,,0,0,0,,你从哪儿来 小鬼\NWhere did you come from, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.94,0:28:05.08,中文,,0,0,0,,还有人在这儿\NSomebody else here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.36,0:28:15.62,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 小心点儿 小鬼\NHey, watch it, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.03,0:28:23.94,中文,,0,0,0,,快走\NVamoose.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.99,0:29:00.42,中文,,0,0,0,,-死路 -搞什么鬼\N- Dead-end. - What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.05,0:29:03.45,中文,,0,0,0,,那些吸血鬼都去哪儿了\NWhere did all the vamps go? Where'd they...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.36,0:29:05.39,中文,,0,0,0,,他们怎么通过的\NHow'd they get through?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.40,0:29:18.96,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我是在捉老鼠的话\NIf I were hunting rats,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.68,0:29:22.20,中文,,0,0,0,,那么这里一定是他们去的地方了\Nthis is exactly where I'd assume they'd go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.20,0:29:23.79,中文,,0,0,0,,或者 这是个陷阱\NOr if this is a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.93,0:29:25.99,中文,,0,0,0,,该死\NGoddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.76,0:30:31.59,中文,,0,0,0,,这边没问题\NAll clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.85,0:30:35.30,中文,,0,0,0,,该死 他们跟着我们\NShit. Behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.53,0:30:37.30,中文,,0,0,0,,走\NGo.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.45,0:30:39.35,中文,,0,0,0,,快走 我拖住他们\NHurry. I'll hold them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.03,0:30:41.48,中文,,0,0,0,,他知道我们在这里了\NHe knows we're here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.48,0:30:44.70,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 那还不快点\NOh well, all the more reason to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.02,0:31:04.84,中文,,0,0,0,,伊弗\NEph?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.77,0:31:08.56,中文,,0,0,0,,伊弗\NEph?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.98,0:31:11.73,中文,,0,0,0,,博士\NDoctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.89,0:31:14.02,中文,,0,0,0,,伊弗 你在吗\NEph, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.96,0:31:15.84,中文,,0,0,0,,搭把手\NGive me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.58,0:31:19.74,中文,,0,0,0,,古德温泽博士\NDr. Goodweather!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.72,0:31:21.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我好冷\NI'm so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.46,0:31:25.31,中文,,0,0,0,,来找我 伊弗 我需要你\NFind me, Eph, I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.56,0:31:27.33,中文,,0,0,0,,-凯莉 -别过去\N- Kelly? - Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.20,0:31:31.22,中文,,0,0,0,,-听我说 -别让他们伤害我\N- Listen to me! - Don't let them hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.46,0:31:33.44,中文,,0,0,0,,博士\NDoctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.60,0:31:34.48,中文,,0,0,0,,不\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.99,0:31:38.16,中文,,0,0,0,,听我说\NListen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.87,0:31:44.48,中文,,0,0,0,,-博士 -那边有事发生了\N- Doctor! - Something's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.77,0:31:47.49,中文,,0,0,0,,光用光拖着他们不能解决问题\NHolding them off with the light isn't gonna get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.83,0:31:58.52,中文,,0,0,0,,走 快走\NGo! Go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.54,0:31:59.29,中文,,0,0,0,,走\NGo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.42,0:32:05.24,中文,,0,0,0,,伊弗\NEph!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.01,0:32:27.76,中文,,0,0,0,,伊弗\NEph!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.54,0:32:33.29,中文,,0,0,0,,伊弗\NEph?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.31,0:33:41.25,中文,,0,0,0,,他们在哪\NWhere are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.09,0:33:45.85,中文,,0,0,0,,我们走\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.64,0:33:58.42,中文,,0,0,0,,伊弗\NEph?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.42,0:34:34.60,中文,,0,0,0,,伊弗 你在哪 快\NEph, where are you? Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.86,0:34:35.99,中文,,0,0,0,,凯莉 我在这\NKelly, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.75,0:34:50.13,中文,,0,0,0,,她在哪里 该死的 来啊\NWhere is she? Goddamn it, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.64,0:34:52.89,中文,,0,0,0,,你们在等什么 来啊\NWhat are you waiting for?! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.85,0:35:24.73,中文,,0,0,0,,你是来毁灭我的吗\NHave you come here to destroy me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.68,0:35:28.33,中文,,0,0,0,,那个老教授\NThe old professor...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.35,0:35:32.07,中文,,0,0,0,,有个了新学生\Nhas a new pupil...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.21,0:35:37.90,中文,,0,0,0,,来送死 像他当年那样\N...to fail... as he failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.96,0:35:45.17,中文,,0,0,0,,我夺走了他所有的一切\NI have taken everything from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.66,0:35:47.87,中文,,0,0,0,,而我\NAnd I...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.95,0:35:50.66,中文,,0,0,0,,也会夺走\Nwill take everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.31,0:35:53.47,中文,,0,0,0,,你的一切\Nfrom you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.12,0:35:56.29,中文,,0,0,0,,你的妻子\NYour wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.66,0:35:59.86,中文,,0,0,0,,你的儿子\Nyour son.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.53,0:36:03.43,中文,,0,0,0,,我\NI...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.51,0:36:07.86,中文,,0,0,0,,是人类的吞噬者\Nam a drinker of men.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.13,0:36:18.67,中文,,0,0,0,,教授\NProfessore.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.21,0:36:47.63,中文,,0,0,0,,马丁斯尼夫人\NMrs. Martinez!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.22,0:36:54.54,中文,,0,0,0,,马丁斯尼夫人\NMrs. Martinez?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.74,0:37:00.37,中文,,0,0,0,,马丁斯尼夫人\NMrs. Martinez?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.27,0:37:09.79,中文,,0,0,0,,马丁斯尼夫人\NMrs. Martinez?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.35,0:37:14.79,中文,,0,0,0,,我给你拿了香烟\NI got your cigarettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.83,0:37:18.00,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 谢谢\NOh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.51,0:37:25.23,中文,,0,0,0,,可爱的小男孩\NSweet young boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.34,0:37:56.44,中文,,0,0,0,,有人看见了吗 他往哪个方向跑的\NDid anyone see? Which way did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.90,0:37:58.63,中文,,0,0,0,,哪条路\NWhich path?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.96,0:38:02.36,中文,,0,0,0,,-我们找到他了 -不 是他找到了我们\N- We had him. - No, he had us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.63,0:38:04.54,中文,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\NAre you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.15,0:38:06.02,中文,,0,0,0,,我没事\NI think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.49,0:38:10.20,中文,,0,0,0,,-你看见他了 -是的 我看见他了\N- You saw him? - Yeah, I saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.42,0:38:11.42,中文,,0,0,0,,我听到了她的声音\NI heard her voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.85,0:38:14.65,中文,,0,0,0,,凯莉\NKelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.91,0:38:17.28,中文,,0,0,0,,她朝着我大喊\NShe was calling out to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.93,0:38:21.92,中文,,0,0,0,,-他戏弄了我 -当然 他戏弄了你\N- He tricked me. - Of course, he tricked you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.11,0:38:23.81,中文,,0,0,0,,你怎么能那样跑掉\NHow could you run off like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.64,0:38:27.49,中文,,0,0,0,,我们差点就要猎捕你而不是猎捕那东西了\NWe ended up hunting for you instead of that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.50,0:38:30.86,中文,,0,0,0,,你为什么要点燃光弹 那东西把他都驱跑了\NWhy did you ignite the light bomb? It chased him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.86,0:38:32.65,中文,,0,0,0,,-我们没得选 -他就在那里\N- We had no choice! - He was right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.65,0:38:35.32,中文,,0,0,0,,就在我咫尺之遥 现在他都跑了\NRight within my grasp! Now gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.68,0:38:44.77,中文,,0,0,0,,除非毁了血祖 否则我不会停下来的\NI'll not rest until the Master is destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.77,0:38:47.60,中文,,0,0,0,,事到如今 他也不会停下来的\NAnd now, neither will he!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.86,0:38:52.51,中文,,0,0,0,,我砸了你  你\NI'll break you, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.28,0:38:55.34,中文,,0,0,0,,食尸鬼\Nstrigoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.54,0:38:58.36,中文,,0,0,0,,杀了你 去死 你去死\NKill you! Die, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.99,0:39:01.24,中文,,0,0,0,,去死 食尸鬼\NDie, strigoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.40,0:39:13.23,中文,,0,0,0,,走这边\NThis way!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.44,0:39:21.00,中文,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道他往这边去\NHow did you know he went this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.00,0:39:22.98,中文,,0,0,0,,血祖就在这附近\NThe Master is here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.87,0:39:25.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我们得找出他在哪里 重新布阵\NWe should think this out, regroup.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.06,0:39:28.50,中文,,0,0,0,,然后再让他们重新布阵 为什么要那样做\NAnd let them regroup? Why would we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.75,0:39:30.69,中文,,0,0,0,,我们可能再也不会有这样的机会了\NWe may never get this chance again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.58,0:39:48.58,中文,,0,0,0,,-该死 -艰难的选择哈\N- God damn it! - Tough choice here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.58,0:39:50.61,中文,,0,0,0,,这只是个基本的随机选择\NThat's basically a random choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.76,0:39:51.57,中文,,0,0,0,,不是\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.24,0:39:54.08,中文,,0,0,0,,听着 我想到了\NLook... I get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.08,0:39:55.93,中文,,0,0,0,,虽然我和你是同一阵线的 但这很疯狂\NI'm on your side, but this is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.93,0:39:57.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我们让他落荒而逃\NWe've got him on the run!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.00,0:39:59.18,中文,,0,0,0,,要乘胜追击 做好你的本分\NWe must press on! Do what you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.18,0:40:00.47,中文,,0,0,0,,-住手 -先等一下\N- Stop! - Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.60,0:40:02.79,中文,,0,0,0,,关掉手电筒\NFlashlights off.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.21,0:40:04.23,中文,,0,0,0,,只开紫外线灯\NUV only.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.97,0:40:10.88,中文,,0,0,0,,看到了吗\NYou see?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.56,0:40:14.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我说的没错 现在 我先走\NI was right! Now, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.20,0:40:17.20,中文,,0,0,0,,停下来 等等 诺拉\NStop! Wait. Nora.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.52,0:40:18.74,中文,,0,0,0,,我们还等什么\NWhat are we waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.00,0:40:42.16,中文,,0,0,0,,那边有很多怪物\NThat's a lot of monsters.
